						<p>In the same verandah, south side.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">Kulōttuṅgachōḷadēva I: Year 40 = 1109-10 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>This incomplete inscription commences with the <hi rend="italic">praśasti, Pugaḻmādu viḷaṅga, etc.,</hi> of the king.</p>						

						<p>It refers to the residents of Iḍaikkuḍi <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Iravikulamāṇikka-nallūr Seṅgaṇi and other villages.</p>						

